name: Remote Depot
LocationDStext: May not deploy to Bespin, Coruscant, Kessel, Ralltiir, or Tatooine. Once per game, may deploy an Effect that deploys on a character or a device here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
LocationLStext: Unless opponent's Sleen or matching operative at same site or related site, those sites are immune to Ounee Ta.
